# GuidedTourTooltip

Welcome to `GuidedTourTooltip` component.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/guided-tour-tooltip
```

```tsx
import { GuidedTourTooltip } from '@ids-ts/guided-tour-tooltip';
```

